flowchart TD
    A{Application type?} --> B[Batch processor]
    A --> C[Long-running service]

    B --> D[System allocator]

    C --> E{Fragmentation<br/>concerns?}

    E -->|No| F{Memory critical?}
    E -->|Yes| G[jemalloc with<br/>aggressive decay]

    F -->|No| H[mimalloc]
    F -->|Yes| I[Capped allocator]

    style D fill:#90EE90,stroke:#228B22
    style G fill:#87CEEB,stroke:#4169E1
    style H fill:#90EE90,stroke:#228B22
    style I fill:#DDA0DD,stroke:#8B008B
